(48, 'Launch Control 3.14: Chasing the Legacy', 'In the Season 3 Finale of Launch Control: David Higgins and Craig Drew represent Subaru at Wales Rally GB, to celebrate the 20th anniversary of the car maker\'s first WRC Championship title', 'https://mcdn.podbean.com/mf/web/k7nc68/SRT2015-Ep14-ChasingTheLegacy2_h264mov-Pod-720.mp4', 'https://pbcdn1.podbean.com/imglogo/ep-logo/pbblog875366/srt2015-eps14-card.jpg', '2015-12-23 07:00:00', '19:37:00', 2913),
